National investigative TV program is looking for examples or cases
of industrial espionage, especially in the high-tech fields (e.g.
aerospace, pharmaceuticals, computing/electronics, optics, etc.)
for a story on economic espionage.  Particularly interested in more
recent cases with international and/or governmental involvement. 
 
Information will be handled with discretion.
 
